task.en: Launch Dictionary, and open the window (usually the about window) that shows its version.
task.zh: 打开词典，打开关于软件，找到展示其版本的那个界面。
task.ar: افتح القاموس وافتح النافذة التي تعرض إصدار التطبيق (عادةً نافذة حول التطبيق).
task.ja: 辞書を起動し、バージョン情報が表示されるウィンドウ（通常は「このソフトウェアについて」のウィンドウ）を開いてください。
task.ru: Запустите приложение Словарь и откройте окно, в котором отображается версия (обычно это окно "О программе").

in_process: osascript -e 'display dialog "View dictionary version, please click here." with title "Hint" buttons {"Cancel", "OK"} default button "OK"'
grading_command: osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep "Dictionary" | grep -q "Version" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep "词典" | grep -q "版本" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep "القاموس" | grep -q "الإصدار" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep "辞書" | grep -q "バージョン" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep "Словарь" | grep -q "Версия" && echo "True" || echo "False"
